snippet.title: "Monster Musume Fantastic Life" releases on G123!
snippet.description:
▼Play now
https://s.g123.jp/gb5qkftj

▼Click here for the latest information
https://g123.jp/news/monmusu?lang=en

▼Click here for G123
https://g123.jp/?lang=en

◆Enjoy your thrilling cohabitation life!"Monster Musume Fantastic Life" is now available on G123!
Enjoy living with over 50 of the cutest monster girls from the comfort of your browser.
Go on dates, bathe in hot springs, and sometimes punish bad guys with your monster girls... an exciting everyday life awaits you!

◆7 Day Login Bonus! Get SSR Ally "Ils" on Day 2!
Log in for 7 days to receive login bonuses! Get SSR Ally "Ils" as a reward on the second day. Don't miss out on this chance to claim so many great rewards.

◆Get SR Girl "Merino" in the Tutorial!
After starting the game, you'll receive SR Girl "Merino" during the tutorial. She will be waiting for you at the Sno Ball Resort. Raise her Charm and Bliss and something good might happen...?! Be sure to check it out in-game.


#MnsterMusume #g123 #FantasticLife #monmusuFL

©OKAYADO/TOKUMA SHOTEN
